# SMTP Email Protocol Module - Facade
# Comprehensive SMTP/MIME implementation for Simple language
# RFC 5321 (SMTP), RFC 5322 (Email), RFC 2045-2049 (MIME)
#
# This is a facade that re-exports all SMTP functionality from submodules:
# - smtp/types.spl: Response codes, session states, response parsing
# - smtp/connect.spl: SMTP protocol commands
# - smtp/send.spl: Email validation, headers, message building
# - smtp/mime.spl: MIME types, boundaries, encoding detection
# - smtp/auth.spl: Authentication encoding
# - smtp/utilities.spl: Base64, quoted-printable encoding

